      "value": "<p>Your covering fire keeps foes from reacting to the battlefield freely, lest they catch a bullet from your suppressing fire.</p><hr /><p><strong>Benefit:</strong> When you successfully provide the benefit of @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JournalEntry.U37n5tY5hn1ctzQL.JournalEntryPage.R33uiOMesYP0ISWl#covering-fire]{covering fire} to an ally, choose one creature in your line of effect. That creature can’t take attacks of opportunity and their readied actions can’t be resolved until the start of their next turn.</p>"
